longBusinessSummary: Gaming Technologies, Inc. operates as a business to business (B2B) early stage gambling industry company in the United States and Mexico. The company develops and publishes mobile games; licenses third-party games for distribution; and operates a proprietary gaming platform that enables B2B partners to establish online gambling presences, as well as operates a regulated online casino and sports betting site through vale.mx. It also intends to license its software platform to mobile gaming operators and developers to enable rapid development of new games. The company was formerly known as Dito, Inc. and changed its name to Gaming Technologies, Inc. in December 2020. Gaming Technologies, Inc. was founded in 2017 and is headquartered in New York, New York.
